{#- DeepSeek-R1-Distill simple-structured template. The runtime applies the
    structured prompt_templates extracted from this jinja (the official template
    has tool/namespace logic minja can't render). DeepSeek format:
    <пљЬbeginвЦБofвЦБsentenceпљЬ>{system}<пљЬUserпљЬ>{user}<пљЬAssistantпљЬ>{response}<пљЬendвЦБofвЦБsentenceпљЬ>.
    BOS (<пљЬbeginвЦБofвЦБsentenceпљЬ>) is added by the runtime start_token; stop =
    <пљЬendвЦБofвЦБsentenceпљЬ> (== eos). The assistant emits <think>вА¶</think> then the
    answer (the model reasons on its own; no <think> is pre-filled). -#}
{%- for message in messages -%}
{%- if message['role'] == 'system' -%}
{{- message['content'] -}}
{%- elif message['role'] == 'user' -%}
{{- '<пљЬUserпљЬ>' + message['content'] -}}
{%- elif message['role'] == 'assistant' -%}
{{- '<пљЬAssistantпљЬ>' + message['content'] + '<пљЬendвЦБofвЦБsentenceпљЬ>' -}}
{%- endif -%}
{%- endfor -%}
{%- if add_generation_prompt -%}
{{- '<пљЬAssistantпљЬ>' -}}
{%- endif -%}
